&kp Q       &mt LALT E  &mt LGUI I  &mt LSHFT A &mt LCTRL O &kp COMMA           &kp G       &mt RCTRL T &mt RSHFT N &mt RGUI S  &mt RALT H  &kp P
            &kp Z       &kp X       &kp C       &kp V                                       &kp D       &kp M       &kp J       &kp B
